title: Persikutim East Kutai
text: Persikutim stand for Persatuan Sepakbola Indonesia Kutai Timur (<a href="English%20language">en</a>: "Football Association of Indonesia East Kutai"). Persikutim East Kutai is an <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Sangatta">Sangatta</a>, <a href="East%20Kutai%20Regency">East Kutai Regency</a>, <a href="East%20Kalimantan">East Kalimantan</a>. They currently compete at <a href="Liga%203%20%28Indonesia%29">Liga 3</a>. Persikutim East Kutai main rivals are <a href="PS%20Mitra%20Kukar">PS Mitra Kukar</a> and <a href="Persikubar%20West%20Kutai">Persikubar West Kutai</a>.
